<!--- Guidance for  download_docs.cfm screen--->

<ul>

<li>The purpose of this screen is to provide a way to download documents during crisis conditions, or for any other reason.</li>
<li>All documents that have been uploaded into this planning tool are displayed on this screen, and may be selected for download.</li>
<li>Only Administrators and Universal Viewers can view this screen.</li>
<li>These Universal Viewers are people selected by the Local Administrators to serve as stand-ins if the Local Administrators are absent during crisis. Universal Viewers will not necessarily have any other role in this on-line planning tool (though they may).</li>

</ul>
